test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[28], [28]]
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: [28]
  Full diff:
  - [[28], [28]]
  + []
test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[28]]
  Right contains one more item: [28]
  Full diff:
  - [[28]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 56 == 28
 +  where 56 = <built-in function prod>([1, 2, 4, 7])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
